Lets review whata codependent means-  a person, role or thing that controls a majority of your life, such as your emotions, your actions, and your attitude. all but one are unhealthy and that one is God. the rest mainly destroy your life.  Cassie and liz. i understand that you want to help him, but you have become obsessed to the point where he is your codependent or his prob is. i might not have any room whatsoever to be talking, but from my observations, he seems to be as much a part of you as you are a part of yourself.  you need to realize that no matter what you do to help, there's only so much that will and the rest is up to God.
